page.title: 02POPULATION SURVEY.
page.content:
{PRIORY MIDDLE SCHOOL}have recently conducted a survey by sending a questionnaire to 147 parents. The questionnaires had different questions on them such as,how many times have you moved house and where you were born.84 people {(57.1%)} replied.1 person {(1.19%)}has lived in Slough without moving.20 people{(23.8%)}were born in Qlough.64 people{(76.1%)}were not born in Slough.5 people{(5.9%)}have moved once.17 people{(20.2%)}have moved twice.21 people{(25.0%)}have moved thrice.15 people{(17.8%)}have moved four times.11 people{(13.0%)}have moved five times.14 people{(16.6%)} have moved more than five times.
